rows.label: qev087507_MSG0001
rows.name:
Well, I'll be damned.
Didn't think you'd solve both problems THAT fast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0007
rows.name: You're your parents' daughter for sure, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0009
rows.name: It's true they were both engineering geniuses.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0010
rows.name:
But they were beloved by people for their
fire and initiative more than their theories.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0011
rows.name: They were heroes for folks in my generation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0012
rows.name:
Can't help but think how much further along
NLA'd be if they were still with us...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0013
rows.name: I'm happy to hear you say that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0014
rows.name: But that job falls on all of us living here now, Commander.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087507_MSG0015
rows.name:
I'm nowhere near their level yet,
but I promise I'll keep doing my best![ST:wait ]
